metadata.name: Diba
metadata.description:
This photo was taken in a modern building named "Namaz Khaneh" made by iranian famous architect "Kamran Diba".
This building is so simple in structure yet so amazing in concept! To me, this structor is a symbol of true minimalism.
This photo was taken in 2019 and uploaded to the "Unsplash" platform days after that. And to this date, it has more than 2 milion views and more than 8000 downloads on that platform.
